e. Let's read through that.\\\", \\\"thinkingSignature\\\": \\\"{\\\\\\\"id\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"rs_05857f5c7c133a070169f61d29d32881948705424a833e7b35\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"type\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"reasoning\\\\\\\",\\\\\\\"encrypted_content\\\\\\\":\\\\\\\"gAAAAABp9h0_qY1bnRg6JxJ2NuJw8ElX24fWR_QV8AAZ4WkZ6CV3xIoYtOspRdfy5UAE9HDxRYqWWTsRaBJWuh9DcRsj5Uv6zgw6kL2suTRXHISOGAUQxLQiHQ2Tve8tI3v0bqCSazEgOsijsFqm4YiXdUa8Ah0yft9c7Br35UFoMDfP1Yuhvt_jb5s4swibeV0-vcTYOt6dDlSkrFCd4W_3-BgD1ISgU-SInYnOFp8wv73uEN2Ve-tjYk5FrW00537RuRlVgV94OL9iT26x6EKYOrvnT2v5Z4CVfOFOIoePLzrEu0PNH3i-WaQZFuivcC6sHt4d17IcMnumvz9oo_dRVCLHSoYH5rDW4EKHRCjYLxZGQ3JykYcSOVmo7GabLCeEkFtQpjsG3IAC0H_BV3VUMLEI7fmMPZuf7oay5Rl26go-Q9spj3iDTPd3JYniWZ_Lrp0udn7ao4Gqlpp_CcbSvVs1YKcRBZGp16uzHG4WV6YdDEWcoWKxESEE2zqc2N_9rr9ZFAFikGLAquJ5sIKUUBHFqrR0dai2C57tI8RfUty8G1G9mk6Wi6V35dASxmFYQsMV6ESyLOyE0nRm5PkZVkjQ9BZsI_MqSUjjrZnQdQDPi-znJ-bQ70z0-48PP8j2HHe8mYmF9d9ogX8tk2pF9YuaAgyFmkjfkdJc_jfRFdO-3k6b-yj-nmcb98DRXgT206oKTi3i7KR3U1ljYXtnZvxj4yuIHGK1lL-hXX4l6S1HhAduyoESX4htaDqqsqUCIaBLPiVcOQJy1iD9tf9BTExzLpFq0fccsG4lFXSG1iC-bORL577P5iU4eu3mCEPcNgdTHbpk5NnzgK4ZbmDDK98xxU2CGj8Httot-fY_oM17-5aWiMeJXwyz1Mv_4Cpc4hQqNGiBbb9AKFFLoAMJ4bBls-6Nj9a8bFY9MJAcNd5uAz9jkdA2GMFstDIoG5JpASNAmYlFXNr7-H_IKTvToRbEOt8PFgJSc2kxHPLBNVkbhR0TcG9BPz7u2-Uw4wUyZ08ismBel3E8AMKi5Fma-s0xC2VGKMDetWmNMBz6AaYEqTDQXcrLs76AHwq-_Y24VnXe3S1FeAXSzw1UF9jfAhvkO84CrCD3qLF8Bl7p1GiKAw-3MfrjF9UBBb9oLpHahQSoJQPFNp-QPgVJOCNoWT0ZwY5laNMdukyACRP9jYyljq-CHHCBUdNbN8q8G_WcR21rX5TEFyue7nFxrunqf9HeKiqAq-44fXbLcR_XZaApQr4Ia872VwalwQtdDCJpvRP95naNXRRIBs3immdANZ8k-GMPXdeZrDd8PavaEX0UYTNvtHEluqEOhsv6CtWsFH2r8GYfo9mRF_q0CYF5qvK0ORarAGnYCqZhK_a-rh5KBJecD6xYvr5GuS0TrKDBwiGLqwL9UXWE9t9AXEU6Re3XcG3EqfU0MnfJs2dZWSReUqDtHqcmSNGVHlNkwEBC9na95em0amI5mLgrona02vr5S8FhZ3OvUVCbhRVFAvaagrugYiFj9aO3iMUGcX4QfqlBNCG_BtV1HtTgyKybjogoBMV3NXBxziTNHyVNf-kPS3IyrGnPQk6ek1Ktly7fXoHPq8WA-C4jdummgY0pbORaver95-9p3zeTEBiRl2r1ndwjCzsL4G_pMg8jOLdQ1IZ2aITWbR-j4lELr_DeN3qI9nEBPTvQnkK2wDmfFQKSXPidt6rYS9w6Bmk1eHnUacvKk3CEZqWwJwAz1pRw4c15d